---
description: LOCK NAVIGATION AND ROUTES
globs: ["app/**/*.{ts,tsx}", "src/router/**/*.{ts,tsx}", "**/*layout*.{ts,tsx}", "**/*routes*.{ts,tsx}"]
alwaysApply: true
---

This is an existing app with working navigation.

Strictly forbidden unless explicitly requested:
- do not rename routes
- do not rename route params
- do not rename screens
- do not move screens between folders
- do not change navigation flow
- do not change tab order
- do not change stack order
- do not change deep links
- do not change redirects
- do not replace the router
- do not change existing path assumptions

Allowed:
- fix navigation bugs only when necessary
- improve route typing
- clean imports
- make minimal safe fixes that do not change app flow

If a requested change would alter navigation behavior, stop and say what would change.

Default behavior:
preserve all navigation exactly.
